/*COALESCE(CAST(CAST(SUBSTR(COALESCE(TRIM(LEAD_ICOLL_1_0.AT_TIME),''),1,8) AS TIME)AS
 VARCHAR(8)), '23:59:59')*/
CASE 
 WHEN COALESCE(CAST(COALESCE(TRIM(LEAD_ICOLL_1_0.AT_TIME),'') AS CHAR(15)),'') <> '' THEN 
 SUBSTR(CAST(COALESCE(TRIM(LEAD_ICOLL_1_0.AT_TIME),'') AS CHAR(15)),1,8) 
 ELSE '00:00:00' 
END
